---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Protocol Unlocked — Thee Rainers">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
  </Fragment>

  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto w-full">

      <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Protocol Unlocked</p>
      <h1 class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[0.85] mb-6">
        The Blueprint<br/>is yours.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-[440px]">
        The PDF opened in your browser. Check your email — a follow-up lands there too. Day 1 starts when you decide it does.
      </p>

      <!-- Primary next step -->
      <div class="border-l-2 border-[#0057FF] pl-6 mb-12">
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/30 text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Do this before your next session</p>
        <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tight text-xl leading-tight mb-3">Know your primary constraint.</p>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-[400px]">
          The 30-day protocol works fastest when you know which lever is holding your system back. The 7-lever audit takes 3 minutes. It tells you exactly where to focus first — and routes you to the right next step.
        </p>
        <a href="/lever-audit-quiz"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#0057FF] text-[#0057FF] bg-transparent px-8 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#0057FF] hover:text-white">
          Take the 7-Lever Audit →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Workshop -->
      <div class="border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-8 mb-[2px]">
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Live Workshop · Saturday, June 27</p>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold mb-2">The Calibration Workshop</p>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/35 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-5">90 minutes. The mechanical structure to hit, exit, and reset — live, with real-time correction on your movement. $197.</p>
        <a href="/workshop"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-[#0A0A0A]/15 text-[#0A0A0A]/40 bg-transparent px-6 py-3 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:border-[#0057FF] hover:text-[#0057FF]">
          Reserve Your Seat →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Private Architecture -->
      <div class="border border-[#6A0DAD]/15 p-8">
        <p class="text-[#6A0DAD] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Application Only</p>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold mb-2">Private Architecture</p>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/35 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-5">The full operating system. Seven levers deployed together, built around your specific structure. For fighters who are ready to build — not just train.</p>
        <a href="/command"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-[#6A0DAD]/25 text-[#6A0DAD]/60 bg-transparent px-6 py-3 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:border-[#6A0DAD] hover:text-[#6A0DAD]">
          See Private Architecture →
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
